(2503, 'K2_SEF_ITEM_URL_CUSTOM_PREFIX_DESC', 'This prefix (word) will be used in front of every K2 item URL. If you use ''story'' for example, all K2 items URLs would display like this ''domain.com/story/123-item-title-alias'', provided you at least have 1 menu item pointing to all K2 categories as your home menu. Handy for blogs or news portals.', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.com_k2.ini'),
