(2567, 'K2_SETTING_THIS_OPTION_WILL_MAKE_THIS_CATEGORY_INHERIT_ALL_PARAMETERS_FROM_ANOTHER_CATEGORY_THUS_YOU_DONT_HAVE_TO_RESET_ALL_OPTIONS_IN_THIS_ONE_IF_THEY_ARE_THE_SAME_WITH_ANOTHER_CATEGORYS_THIS_SETTING_IS_VERY_USEFUL_WHEN_YOU_ARE_CREATING_CHILD_CATEGORIES_', 'Setting this option will make this category inherit all parameters from another category, thus you don''t have to re-set all options in this one if they are the same with another category''s. This setting is very useful when you are creating child categories which share the same parameters with their parent category, e.g. in the case of a catalog or a news portal/magazine.', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.com_k2.ini'),
