(7585, 'T3_TOUR_INTRO_2', 'Are you ready to discover the best framework for Joomla! yet? Click the buttons below to start your travel and having fun!', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
