(7629, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_17_CONTENT', 'The tab includes settings of the Megamenu - a missing feature in Joomla!. With Megamenu, you can create any type of menu that your site needs.', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
