(7634, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_20_TITLE', 'Module Positions Setting', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
(7635, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_20_CONTENT', '<div class=''t3-admin-tour-img''><img src=''http://joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/jat3v3-documents/tour-guide/layout.png'' alt='''' /></div><p>Using the button to assign module position to the block.</p><div class=''t3-admin-tour-img''><img src=''http://joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/jat3v3-documents/tour-guide/layout-module.png'' alt='''' /></div><p>You can set the number of module positions for a spotlight block.</p>', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
(7636, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_21_TITLE', 'Module Positions', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
(7637, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_21_CONTENT', 'Select the positions that are going to be used in the above selected layout. In other words, this will allow you to freely configure which content to be displayed in that specific selected layout according to your preferences.', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
(7638, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_22_TITLE', 'Responsive Layout', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
(7639, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_22_CONTENT', '<div class=''t3-admin-tour-img''><img src=''http://joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/jat3v3-documents/tour-guide/responsive-layout.png'' alt='''' /></div><p>In this setting panel, you can enable/disable and resize the module positions for the spotlight blocks only for each specific layout: wide, mobile, tablet, etc.</p>', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
(7640, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_23_TITLE', 'Layouts Configuration', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
(7641, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_23_CONTENT', '<div class=''t3-admin-tour-img''><img src=''http://joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/jat3v3-documents/tour-guide/enable-disable-position.png'' alt='''' /></div><p>Using the icon to enable/disable the module position for the spotlight block in the current layout.</p><div class=''t3-admin-tour-img''><img src=''http://joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/jat3v3-documents/tour-guide/resize-module-position.png'' alt='''' /></div><p>Drag to resize the module position (basegrid: 12). Please do keep in mind that it is applied in the current modifying layout only and not applied to all unless you make changes in each layout accordingly.</p>', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
(7642, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_25_TITLE', 'Navigation Configuration', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
(7643, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_25_CONTENT', '<div class=''t3-admin-tour-img''><img src=''http://joomlart.s3.amazonaws.com/images/jat3v3-documents/tour-guide/navigation-setting.png'' alt='''' /></div><p>This place let you set the behavior of the main navigation bar. It also let you choose a cool feature of T3 - Megamenu and its options.</p>', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
(7644, 'T3_TOUR_GUIDE_26_TITLE', 'Option to open sub-menu', '/home/networksoftcom/public_html/administrator/language/en-GB/en-GB.plg_system_t3.ini'),
